description:
With free Mobile Banking from America First, you can perform financial transactions on the go—without making a trip to the credit union. Access Mobile Banking with the same secure credentials as Online Banking, and all of your features are optimized specifically for your iPhone. 

Account information: 
-Check your America First account balances. 
-View your recent activity—including transaction details and pending charges. 
-Log in to multiple America First accounts. 
-Transfer money within your own accounts or to other America First accounts. 

Mobile Deposit: 
-Deposit checks with the camera in your device.

Bill Pay: 
-Schedule, cancel, or modify bills from your device using our free service. 
-Access the billers you are using in Online Banking. 

Person-to-person payments: 
-Enroll in our Popmoney service through Online Banking and use your device to send funds to others via text message or email. 

ABCDeals:
-Get cash back for many of the purchases you’re already making. Just use your America First Visa® debit and credit cards when you buy and your money will be automatically deposited-there’s no limit to the amount you can earn. New offers appear in your Mobile Banking app. Simply activate, buy, and collect!
-Activate your exclusive offers by clicking the icons located in Mobile Banking’s ABCDeals section.  
-Buy using your America First Visa® debit and credit cards at the merchants you’ve activated.
-Collect your cash—it will be automatically deposited in your account.  

Mobile Loan Application
-Apply for a vehicle loan, personal loan, RV loan, line of credit, or Visa® credit card.  
-Our vehicle locator will search a nationwide dealer inventory.  
-Use the VIN scanning tool to value vehicles and capture information.  

Find locations and contact America First: 
-Quickly find the nearest America First branches or ATMs. 
-Speak with a representative over the phone. 

Privacy Policy: https://www.americafirst.com/about/disclosures/membership-agreement.cfm#privacyPolicy 

Terms and Conditions: https://www.americafirst.com/about/disclosures/mobile-banking-service-agreement.cfm 

Mobile Banking users must enroll in Online Banking. Deposits are subject to verification and are not available for immediate withdrawal. See terms in app for limits/availability and other restrictions. 
Some features are only available for eligible members and member accounts. 
America First Mobile Banking is free to use, but messaging and data rates apply.
